.contact-ctrl
   
   .map-wrapper.container-fluid
      .row
         iframe(width="100%" height="300" frameborder="0" style="border:0" src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed/v1/place?q=10019%205th%20Avenue%2C%20New%20York%2C%20NY%2C%20United%20States&key=AIzaSyBN4KolxZV7FOcOTnU2qL4z_UDggGPMTmA")

   .welcome-wrapper.container
      .row
         .col-md-12
            .page-header
               h3 ALOHA!
            P Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur. Excepteur sint occaecat cupidatat non proident, sunt in culpa qui officia deserunt mollit anim id est laborum. Sed ut perspiciatis unde omnis iste natus error sit voluptatem accusantium doloremque laudantium, totam rem aperiam, eaque ipsa quae ab illo inventore veritatis et quasi architecto .

   .address-wrapper.container
      .row
         .col-sm-4(ng-repeat="address in model.addressList track by address.id")
            h5
               span.fa.fa-map-marker.icon
               span {{address.name}}
            address
               div {{address.address}}
               div {{address.tel1}}
               div {{address.tel2}}
               a(href="javascript:void(0)") {{address.email}}

   form.form-wrapper.container(ng-submit="send()")
      .row
         .col-md-12
            .page-header
               h3 Send us a message!

      .row(ng-if="model.isSuccessDisplayed") 
         .col-md-12
            .alert.alert-success You have successfully sent your comment!

      .row(ng-if="model.errorList.length")
         .col-md-12
            .alert.alert-danger
               ul
                  li(ng-repeat="error in model.errorList") {{error}}

      .row
         .col-sm-4
            .form-group
               label First Name (required)
               input.form-control(ng-model="model.firstName" type="text")
         .col-sm-4
            .form-group
               label Last Name (required)
               input.form-control(ng-model="model.lastName" type="text")
         .col-sm-4
            .form-group
               label Email (required)
               input.form-control(ng-model="model.email" type="email")
      .row
         .col-sm-12
            .form-group
               label Comment (required)
               textarea.form-control(ng-model="model.comment" rows="6")
      .row
         .col-sm-2.col-xs-12
            button.btn.btn-block.btn-primary(type="submit" ng-disabled="model.isSuccessDisplayed") Send

